# plot temperatures over time
ggplot(data=df, aes(x=datetime, y=temp_f)) +
  geom_line(size=0.5) +
  geom_point(size=1.0) +
  ggtitle('Temperature')

# plot the number of records by weather condition
ggplot(data = df, mapping = aes(x = weather)) +
  geom_bar(aes(fill = weather)) +
  ggtitle("Weather conditions")
